{"tid":1582401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］如何應對921","createTime":"2019-09-20T04:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T07:04:54.000Z","uid":96148,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"29bf8b46b1b67173d28794b202bda1687b34f4ac","tid":1582401,"uid":96148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:48:09.000Z","msg":"知好多位手足星期六打算出獅鳥<br />\n今日我老豆獻左條計，俾大家集思廣益下<br />\n既然何妖吹大雞，中共又準備晒維穩費俾清潔工，咁我地愛國市民梗係要從旁監督，一路拍片力證佢地對國家的忠誠，一路大大聲叫佢地清得乾淨d，少少渣都唔可以留，牆上仲有膠紙漬？大力d鏟啦柒頭，唔係點對得住國家，對得住三千蚊人工，點同呀爺交待？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好俾埋垃圾膠袋佢地，要佢地將個場執到一塵不染，地下有dd紙碎，都call食環檢控亂拋垃圾<br />\n星期日大家就可以準備返又靚又新鮮的文宣，貼返喺中共特派清潔工幫我地準備好的乾淨牆上面，諗起都興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5940139a5e768ee0686284901875e60b864b69c0","tid":1582401,"uid":96148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:48:17.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"442dc5d82378a237d188d9ae9fc2f96a1e3c675d","tid":1582401,"uid":96148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:48:27.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"ec5e33b2282f1d05996837e386fe08c395925a77","tid":1582401,"uid":96148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:48:38.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"da950b04a704e5819ccb15b0d191dae3a82ed678","tid":1582401,"uid":96148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:48:48.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"3bf956c77ec99c8d3b5172276a96c3361023c084","tid":1582401,"uid":96148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:48:59.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"115d87f2edd8b942175ec6fa8fa19dad8e6c6e52","tid":1582401,"uid":96148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0